      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a major restoration project or a reliable source of spare parts. It currently suffers from significant mechanical failure, including an engine that does not turn over and advanced signs of rust on the undercarriage. The interior shows heavy wear and several electrical components are non-functional. It will need to be towed from the premises, but it offers a solid foundation for those with the skills to rebuild it.",
