    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine runs smoothly and reliably, making it an excellent choice for a daily driver. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, though you will find some minor signs of normal use on the upholstery. The exterior paint still holds a nice shine, despite a few small surface scratches and minor stone chips typical for its age. Overall, it is a dependable, honest car that is ready for its next owner.",
