    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to enjoy a fantastic driving experience with this well-maintained beauty! It\u2019s in good condition, showing pride of ownership with a clean interior and a smooth, reliable ride that you can count on. This car is the perfect blend of quality and value, ready to take you on your next adventure with confidence!",
